<i>adverb</i>: 오죽이나 [오주기나], 오죽 [오죽], 얼마나 [얼마나], 어찌 [어찌], 어쩜 [어쩜], 어쩌면 [어쩌면], 어이 [어이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오죽이나 [오주기나]</dt><br>
<dd>how; really; how much</dd><br>
<dd>(강조하는 말로) 오죽.</dd><br>
<dd>(emphasizing form) Indeed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오죽 [오죽]</dt><br>
<dd>how; really; how much</dd><br>
<dd>동작의 강도가 세거나 상태의 정도가 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With the strong intensity of an action or to a severe degree.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>얼마나 [얼마나]</dt><br>
<dd>1. how</dd><br>
<dd>상태나 느낌 등의 정도가 매우 크고 대단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a great and enormous degree in terms of a state or feeling.</dd><br>
<dd>2. how</dd><br>
<dd>어느 정도나.</dd><br>
<dd>How much.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어찌 [어찌]</dt><br>
<dd>1. why</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 이유로.</dd><br>
<dd>For what reason.</dd><br>
<dd>2. how</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 방법으로. 또는 어떤 방식으로.</dd><br>
<dd>In what method; in what way.</dd><br>
<dd>3. at a certain angle</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 관점에서.</dd><br>
<dd>From a certain point of view.</dd><br>
<dd>4. so much</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 강도나 정도가 대단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a great degree or with a strong intensity.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어쩜 [어쩜]</dt><br>
<dd>1. maybe; perhaps; possibly</dd><br>
<dd>확실하지는 않지만 짐작하건대.</dd><br>
<dd>Not sure but presumably.</dd><br>
<dd>2. how; what</dd><br>
<dd>도대체 어떻게 해서.</dd><br>
<dd>How on earth, as if one cannot believe it.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어쩌면 [어쩌면]</dt><br>
<dd>1. maybe; perhaps; possibly</dd><br>
<dd>확실하지는 않지만 짐작하건대.</dd><br>
<dd>Not sure but presumably.</dd><br>
<dd>2. how; what</dd><br>
<dd>도대체 어떻게 해서.</dd><br>
<dd>How on earth.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어이 [어이]</dt><br>
<dd>how; why</dd><br>
<dd>(옛 말투로) 어찌.</dd><br>
<dd>(old-fashioned) How.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>